    "rich_text_iNwtPR": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "paragraph_g986cQ": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "paragraph_text": "<p>A good night’s sleep does wonders for your mood and overall health. Our nighttime products can help you sleep your way to better skin. Add these coveted overnight essentials to your bedtime rituals and wake up refreshed and beautiful with healthy, glowing skin.</p><br>\n\n<p>Start your nighttime skincare routine with our <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/ocean-cleanser\" class=\"link\">Ocean Cleanser</a>, a seaweed-infused cleanser that clarifies, purifies, and exfoliates to give you radiant skin. Follow with one of our overnight serums to give your complexion a healthy dose of seaweed-derived nutrients and moisture for smoother, plumper, younger-looking skin. </p><br>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/dream-night-serum\" class=\"link\">Dream Night Serum</a> is a powerful seaweed-infused formula combining two firming peptides + algae-derived bio retinol. This serum visibly reduces crow’s feet, fine lines, wrinkles &amp; even deeper wrinkles as your skin ages!</p><br>\n\n<p>After cleansing and treating, slather on a layer of <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/dream-night-cream\" class=\"link\">Dream Night Cream</a>. This rich, hydrating cream is clinically proven to reduce the effects of stress on your skin while you sleep, helping to reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles so you wake up with glowing, youthful-looking skin. The ultra-hydrating formula contains powerful ingredients, including bio-retinol derived from algae and five vital hydrators, including squalane, shea butter, and glycerin.</p><br>\n\n<p>Want to target the signs of aging around your eyes? Roll on our award-winning <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/ocean-eyes\" class=\"link\">Ocean Eyes® Age-Defying Serum</a> to reduce puffiness, followed by a layer of the <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/advanced-repair-eye-cream\" class=\"link\">Advanced Repair Eye Cream</a>, which is packed with plant-derived ingredients that reduce the look of fine lines and bags.</p><br>\n<p>Don’t forget to include body care in your bedtime routine. Lock in moisture with some anti-aging <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/undaria-algae-body-butter\" class=\"link\">Undaria Algae™ Body Butter</a> or get glowing with <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/undaria-algae-oil\" class=\"link\">Undaria Algae™ Body Oil</a>. Finally, spritz some calming <a href=\"https://oseamalibu.com/products/vagus-nerve-pillow-mist\" class=\"link\">Vagus Nerve Pillow Mist</a> on your pillow and drift off to dreamland.</p>",
            "paragraph_classes": ""
          }
        }
      },
